              'features.i18n.subtitle',
              'Multi-language, RTL support, and locale-aware formatting baked into the core.'
            )}
          />
          <FeatureCard
            icon={<BarChart3 />}
            title={t('features.analytics.title', 'Real-time Analytics')}
            subtitle={t(
              'features.analytics.subtitle',
              'Understand your users with live dashboards, funnels, and cohort analysis.'
